    {
      "card": {
        "bgColor": "var(--gray-3)",
        "label": "Lesson 20 • Talking About a Brown Noser",
        "descriptions": [
          {
            "description": "Nearly every office has one: the brown noser. He or she will do just about anything to win favor with the boss. Here Tony, Karen, and Nancy complain about their local brown noser, Mitch."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Tony: "
            },
            {
              "text": "I was just in a meeting with Mitch and Bill. Mitch said to Bill, “Bill, we’re so lucky to have you as our boss. You’re such a great leader!”"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Karen: "
            },
            {
              "text": "He’s "
            },
            {
              "mark": "up to his old tricks"
            },
            {
              "text": ". He’s up to his old tricks. He was trying to earn "
            },
            {
              "mark": "brownie points"
            },
            {
              "text": " with Bill."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Nancy: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Mitch has the reputation of being a "
            },
            {
              "mark": "yes man"
            },
            {
              "text": " and a brown noser. He’s an expert at kissing up."
            },
            {
              "text": "Mitch has the reputation of being a yes man and a brown noser. He’s an expert at "
            },
            {
              "mark": "kissing up"
            },
            {
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Tony: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Then he said to Bill, “Other people here don’t appreciate you like I do!” "
            },
            {
              "mark": "Talk about"
            },
            {
              "text": " trying to "
            },
            {
              "mark": "butter up"
            },
            {
              "text": " the boss!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Nancy: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Yeah, and this time "
            },
            {
              "mark": "at our expense"
            },
            {
              "text": "! He’s just "
            },
            {
              "mark": "out for himself"
            },
            {
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Karen: "
            },
            {
              "text": " Well, it’s a "
            },
            {
              "mark": "dog-eat-dog world"
            },
            {
              "text": ". Obviously he thinks this is the way to "
            },
            {
              "mark": "get ahead"
            },
            {
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Tony: "
            },
            {
              "text": "I guess it’s one way to "
            },
            {
              "mark": "climb the corporate ladder"
            },
            {
              "text": ". But I could never "
            },
            {
              "mark": "look at myself in the mirror"
            },
            {
              "text": " after behaving that way."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Karen: "
            },
            {
              "text": "I’m not good at "
            },
            {
              "mark": "kissing up"
            },
            {
              "text": ". "
            },
            {
              "mark": "No wonder"
            },
            {
              "text": " I’ve been in the same lousy position for 10 years!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Talking About a Brown Noser, Part 2: When You’re Overheard"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Mitch: "
            },
            {
              "text": " Hey guys. Don’t you know it’s rude to "
            },
            {
              "mark": "talk behind someone’s back"
            },
            {
              "text": "? I just overheard your entire conversation!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Tony: "
            },
            {
              "text": " Sorry, Mitch. We didn’t mean to offend you."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Mitch: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Well, "
            },
            {
              "mark": "the walls have ears"
            },
            {
              "text": ". "
            },
            {
              "mark": "Think twice"
            },
            {
              "text": " before you insult me again!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Nancy: "
            },
            {
              "mark": "Chill out"
            },
            {
              "text": "! We were talking about a different Mitch, not you."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Tony: "
            },
            {
              "text": " That’s right. We were talking about Mitch Schneider, over in the accounting department."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Mitch: "
            },
            {
              "mark": " Likely story"
            },
            {
              "text": ". "
            },
            {
              "mark": "I wasn’t born yesterday"
            },
            {
              "mark": "!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
